00:20:06,020 --> 00:20:09,340
 and nothing else, you're really missing out

462
00:20:09,340 --> 00:20:12,300
 on the full picture of what it means

463
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:15,340
 to be part of a body of Christ,

464
00:20:15,340 --> 00:20:19,900
 to be a Christian, to be a follower of Jesus.

465
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:21,080
 Right, and this isn't a guilt trip

466
00:20:21,080 --> 00:20:24,220
 'cause we need volunteers for JCA and VBS, all right?

467
00:20:24,220 --> 00:20:27,000
 I'm not, I'm just saying what the Bible is teaching us,

468
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,220
 okay, it's not.

469
00:20:28,220 --> 00:20:32,200
 So if you don't know the question,

470
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:35,880
 you know, how do I find my spiritual gift?

471
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:37,120
 Again, it's a good question,

472
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:38,780
 and we can talk about this all day.

473
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:42,940
 Let me just give a few practical pointers in this direction.

474
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:46,880
 First of all, okay, don't treat it like an enneagram

475
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,320
 or a disc or a Myers-Briggs,

476
00:20:48,320 --> 00:20:50,940
 one of those personality tests, that kind of stuff, okay?

477
00:20:50,940 --> 00:20:54,220
 Your spiritual gift is not a personality test, all right?

478
00:20:54,220 --> 00:20:57,120
 I mean, there are online tools that might be useful,

479
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:59,940
 but I wouldn't even start there necessarily.

480
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:02,740
 The first step to finding out your part

481
00:21:02,740 --> 00:21:07,740
 and your gift in the body of Christ is to seek God first.

482
00:21:07,740 --> 00:21:09,960
 Seek first the kingdom and all these other things

483
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,960
 will then be given to you.

484
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:14,960
 Right, this means reading your Bible,

485
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:16,900
 this means prayer and fasting,

486
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:19,500
 this means constant confession and repentance,

487
00:21:19,500 --> 00:21:21,840
 this means developing and nurturing

488
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:24,280
 your relationship with Jesus.

489
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:27,040
 That's the first basic step.

490
00:21:27,040 --> 00:21:29,360
 The second step is this, right?

491
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:30,800
 When you're following Jesus,

492
00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:32,800
 when you know that your heart

493
00:21:32,800 --> 00:21:35,600
 and the desires of your heart have been made pure,

494
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:39,240
 then you ask, ask the Holy Spirit to show you,

495
00:21:39,240 --> 00:21:42,520
 where do you want me to serve?

496
00:21:42,520 --> 00:21:44,700
 What is the gift that you've given me?

497
00:21:44,700 --> 00:21:48,760
 What is my part in the body of Christ?

498
00:21:48,760 --> 00:21:51,800
 And scripture tells us that when we do that,

499
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:56,800
 if we ask anything according to his will, he will hear us.

500
00:21:56,800 --> 00:22:02,620
 One good way to ask is to ask those around you,

501
00:22:02,620 --> 00:22:04,100
 the people that you trust around you,

502
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:05,480
 the other people that you know

503
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:09,060
 are also in the same journey of following Jesus.

504
00:22:09,060 --> 00:22:11,080
 Find a community that you trust,

505
00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:12,940
 talk to people, come along with them and say,

506
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:15,780
 hey, you know, I feel like God has given me a gift

507
00:22:15,780 --> 00:22:18,180
 in whatever, do you see that in me?

508
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:20,560
 Or maybe ask one of your leaders at the church

509
00:22:20,560 --> 00:22:22,400
 or whatever, say, I feel like I have the gift of this.

