 This is Pentecost Sunday, and this is exactly

829
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:23,240
 what happens on the day of Pentecost

830
00:38:23,240 --> 00:38:26,860
 when the Holy Spirit first fell upon the followers.

831
00:38:26,860 --> 00:38:29,520
 This is a beautiful picture of gifts and fruit

832
00:38:29,520 --> 00:38:32,720
 coming together when the early church is first established.

833
00:38:32,720 --> 00:38:36,440
 Acts 2.43 tells us this, that when the Holy Spirit came,

834
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:40,040
 everybody was filled with awe at the many wonders

835
00:38:40,040 --> 00:38:43,300
 and signs being performed by the apostles.

836
00:38:43,300 --> 00:38:46,680
 These are the spiritual gifts at work, tongues, healing,

837
00:38:46,680 --> 00:38:49,260
 all these things that the apostles began to minister

838
