 They sold property and possessions

843
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:02,040
 and gave to anyone in need.

844
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:04,480
 They continued to meet together in temple courts,

845
00:39:04,480 --> 00:39:08,360
 broke bread, ate together with glad and sincere hearts,

846
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:11,560
 praising God and enjoying the favor of all the people.

847
00:39:11,560 --> 00:39:14,080
 And the Lord added to the number daily

848
00:39:14,080 --> 00:39:15,720
 those who were being saved.

849
00:39:16,640 --> 00:39:20,380
 This is the fruit of the Spirit beginning to grow.

850
00:39:20,380 --> 00:39:24,540
 Gifts and fruit, that's how the Holy Spirit

851
00:39:24,540 --> 00:39:29,120
 has always wanted to work, has always been working,

852
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:32,520
 and how he desires to continue to work today.

